data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5,000 concession towards buyers' closing costs or interest rate buy down. WOW! Awesome price for this SUPER CUTE all brick, open concept home in the highly sought after gated community of Villages of Fireside. This beauty features vaulted ceilings, split floorplan, stainless steel appliances & updates throughout. Kitchen overlooks the large family room that is perfect for entertaining.  You can host holidays & enjoy back yard BBQs in your large back yard. Sip your coffee in the mornings on your back patio or roast s'mores on a firepit under the stars at night. Yard has room for boat/RV. The best part about living in Villages of Fireside is you get to enjoy access to the private community dock on black creek where you can go to relax all of your worries away. Enjoy fishing, swimming, kayaking, rope swinging and more. NO CDD FEES! District for the sought after Clay County Schools. Convenient to shopping, dining, churches and the new toll road connector. Roof replaced 2017. HVAC 2016. Key features include: Ring cameras. Security system. Termite Bond. Large yard. Full rain gutter system. All brick. Pond view and access in back yard. Gated community with dock access to black creek. Open floorplan. Come make this your Home Sweet Home!
